title: Microsoft Azure SQL Databases: Storage
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the amount of storage used by an azure database.
 You can configure levels for the percentage using the rule "Azure Databases".

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each database if all required metrics
 (average_storage_percent) are given.
